PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1771902191
OL,3,CMandelson questioned by police after
OL,4,Carrest on suspicion of misconduct in
OL,5,Coffice
OL,7,FThe Liberal Democrats will, meanwhile,
OL,8,Fseek to force the public release of
OL,9,Ffiles relating to Andrew Mountbatten-
OL,10,FWindsor's appointment as a trade
OL,11,Fenvoy, as the former prince too faces
OL,12,Faccusations of sharing sensitive
OL,13,Finformation with Epstein while in the
OL,14,Frole.
OL,16,FFootage showed Lord Mandelson being
OL,17,Fled out of his house by a plain
OL,18,Fclothes police officer on Monday and
OL,19,Fthe Metropolitan Police later said the
OL,20,F72-year-old was taken to a London
OL,21,Fpolice station for interview.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
