OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1771902191
OL,3,CMandelson questioned by police after
OL,4,Carrest on suspicion of misconduct in
OL,5,Coffice
OL,7,FTwo of his properties were previously
OL,8,Fsearched by police in connection with
OL,9,Fthe allegations, which surfaced
OL,10,Ffollowing the US Department of
OL,11,FJustice's document dump related to
OL,12,FEpstein last month.
OL,14,FAs part of the so-called Epstein
OL,15,Ffiles, emails from 2009 appear to show
OL,16,FLord Mandelson pass on an assessment
OL,17,Fby Gordon Brown's adviser of potential
OL,18,Fpolicy measures including an "asset
OL,19,Fsales plan".
OL,26,@zD@^OU{D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
