CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1771902191
OL,3,CMandelson questioned by police after
OL,4,Carrest on suspicion of misconduct in
OL,5,Coffice
OL,7,FHe also appeared to discuss a tax on
OL,8,Fbankers' bonuses and confirm an
OL,9,Fimminent bailout package for the euro
OL,10,Fthe day before it was announced in
OL,11,F2010.
OL,13,FThe emails appeared to be sent to
OL,14,FEpstein after he became a convicted
OL,15,Fsex offender.
OL,17,FIt is understood the Crown Prosecution
OL,18,FService is yet to offer any early
OL,19,Finvestigative advice in relation to
OL,20,Fthe allegations against Lord Mandelson.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
