OL,3,CMandelson questioned by police after
OL,4,Carrest on suspicion of misconduct in
OL,5,Coffice
OL,7,FThe Cabinet Office previously referred
OL,8,Fmaterial to police in connection with
OL,9,Fthe probe into Lord Mandelson after an
OL,10,Finitial review of the Epstein files
OL,11,Fsuggested "safeguards were
OL,12,Fcompromised".
OL,14,FThe arrest came shortly after MPs were
OL,15,Ftold the first tranche of documents
OL,16,Frelated to Lord Mandelson's
OL,17,Fappointment as US ambassador is
OL,18,Fexpected to be released in early March.
OL,26,@sD@KOUtD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
