OL,3,CMandelson questioned by police after
OL,4,Carrest on suspicion of misconduct in
OL,5,Coffice
OL,7,FChief Secretary to the Prime Minister,
OL,8,FDarren Jones, said some of the
OL,9,Fcorrespondence between Downing Street
OL,10,Fand the peer will be delayed "because
OL,11,Fof the Metropolitan Police interest".
OL,13,FThe Prime Minister previously said the
OL,14,Ffiles will prove Lord Mandelson lied
OL,15,Fduring the vetting process before
OL,16,Ftaking on the ambassador role.
OL,26,@rD@^OUsD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
