OL,3,CMandelson questioned by police after
OL,4,Carrest on suspicion of misconduct in
OL,5,Coffice
OL,7,FFollowing the release of the Epstein
OL,8,Ffiles, Lord Mandelson said he has "no
OL,9,Frecollection" of receiving payments
OL,10,Ftotalling 75,000 dollars (about
OL,11,F#55,000) from Epstein between 2003 and
OL,12,F2004 as bank details in the documents
OL,13,Findicated.
OL,15,FEpstein is also said to have paid for
OL,16,Fan osteopathy course for Lord
OL,17,FMandelson's husband, Reinaldo Avila Da
OL,18,FSilva, in 2009, at the time the
OL,19,Fgovernment was dealing with the
OL,20,Ffinancial crisis.
OL,26,@pD@cOUqD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
