OL,3,CMandelson questioned by police after
OL,4,Carrest on suspicion of misconduct in
OL,5,Coffice
OL,7,FLord Mandelson's arrest comes days
OL,8,Fafter Andrew was taken into custody on
OL,9,Fsuspicion of misconduct in public
OL,10,Foffice.
OL,12,FThe former prince was released under
OL,13,Finvestigation.
OL,15,FDespite being stripped of his title
OL,16,Flast year, the former duke of York is
OL,17,Fstill eighth in line to the throne,
OL,18,Fand an Act of Parliament would be
OL,19,Frequired to remove Andrew and prevent
OL,20,Fhim from ever becoming king.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
