PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1771902191
OL,3,CMandelson questioned by police after
OL,4,Carrest on suspicion of misconduct in
OL,5,Coffice
OL,7,FThe UK Government will consider
OL,8,Fintroducing such legislation once
OL,9,Fpolice have finished their
OL,10,Finvestigation into the King's
OL,11,Fdisgraced brother, the Press
OL,12,FAssociation understands.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
