CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1771902191
OL,3,CMandelson questioned by police after
OL,4,Carrest on suspicion of misconduct in
OL,5,Coffice
OL,7,FThe Lib Dems will table a humble
OL,8,Faddress in the Commons ` the same
OL,9,Farcane mechanism the Tories used to
OL,10,Fpress for the release of files on Lord
OL,11,FMandelson's appointment as ambassador
OL,12,F` in a bid to compel the Government to
OL,13,Fdisclose information about Andrew, who
OL,14,Fserved as a trade envoy between 2001
OL,15,Fand 2011.
OL,17,FThe motion will call for the release
OL,18,Fof papers relating to Andrew's
OL,19,Fappointment to the post, including any
OL,20,Fvetting and any correspondence from
OL,21,FLord Mandelson.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
